Fronthaul Network Intelligence System - Frontend Build
Phase 1: Project Setup & Core Infrastructure
 Initialize Vite + React + TypeScript project in Frontend folder
 Configure custom Tailwind with design system tokens
 Add Google Fonts (Geist Mono, Inter, IBM Plex Mono)
 Create base CSS with design tokens
Phase 2: Layout & Navigation
Build command center layout structure (header, left rail, main canvas, right panel, footer)..doing before model expired
 Implement keyboard shortcuts (H, T, P, ESC)
 Create view mode switching (Explore, Focus, Compare, Timeline)
Phase 3: Interactive Heatmap (Centerpiece)
 Build canvas-based similarity heatmap with D3 color scale
 Implement cell hover states (tooltip, row/column highlight)
 Implement cell click behavior (isolation, comparison mode)
 Add crosshair cursor
Phase 4: Topology Force Graph
 Integrate D3-force or react-force-graph-2d
 Custom node rendering (groups, anomalies with pulse)
 Edge rendering (thickness by similarity, opacity by confidence)
 Hover/click interactions (zoom, focus, expand)
Phase 5: Propagation Flow Diagram
 Build Sankey-inspired SVG flow visualization
 Time axis with flow animations
 Flow state coloring (healthy, degraded, critical)
Phase 6: Intelligence Panel
 LLM insights streaming component (character-by-character)
 Recommendation cards
 Anomaly list with dot notation status
Phase 7: Supporting Features
